summary:
Bonjour ,
Je suis auto-entrepreneur dans la garde d'enfants, je dispose d'une expérience de 3ans ,je suis une jeune femme responsable,attachante et très protectrice envers les enfants. J'aide et contribue à l'évolution des enfants en leurs proposant des activités, en les aidant au mieux à se sentir bien et en confiance .

Last October 2017, I move to UK to do study masters on my profession while doing the studies I work in Burger King Cardiff part time and in PENYLAN Care Home as Care assistant.
I worked with the elderly in in Care Homes, bath, feed them, assist them to toilet, and help them get dressed. Also assist them in doing recreational activities. (December 2017 to July 2018)

I had worked with different walks of life and state of health and mind with the elderly people. Assist them in bath or bed bath, prepare their drinks like coffee or tea, and feed them on residents that need help on taking food. Assist them to toilets if residents will like to go to toilet rather than have nappies on or change nappies if residents can’t manage to go to the toilet. (April 2018 to July 2018)

Assist them when going to any recreational actirespectike painting, gardening, playing scrabble, watching concerts within the home.
Monitor their food intake and fluids, Put them to bed and give them all the care and respect needed.

I attend to many babysitting from months to teenagers. I have been doing babysitting, with different nationalities. British, French, Lebanesse, Spanish, Americans. I love being with kids, attend to their needs and give them extra care as babysitter/nanny/childcare as if I am their own child. Reliable, hardworking honest Filipina who is available to do very special care to any child I am into.

I am looking for a babysitting night work.

Hello families!

I’m Hannah, I’m originally from Ohio and am now based in Paris. I'm only available in the evenings and on the weekend. 

I have been working with children consistently for the past 10 years in both a professional and residential capacity. I have a Bachelor’s Degree in Elementary Educational Studies and have spent many hours in both classrooms, daycares, and summer camps. I have experience with ages ranging from newborns to teenagers.

Currently, I work in a bilingual nursery in Paris with children from newborn to 2 years old. Besides the foundational care involved with children of this age (diapering, feeding, cuddles, changing) my main role is to engage the kids in developmentally appropriate activities that stimulate them and expose them to the English language. We plan fine motor activities such as sticker collages and finger painting and do lots of singing and dancing. 

Before this position, I worked five years as a nanny for three french children now aged 3, 5, and 7. I was their main caregiver in the evenings, as well as on holidays abroad. This role involved preparing meals, accompanying the kids to their activities and medical appointments, and teaching them English.

summary:

Je me suis occupée de petites filles et de petits garçons, et j'adore jouer avec eux tout en leur apprenant de nouvelles choses. Je suis à l'écoute et je sais m'adapter à la personnalité de chaque enfant. Je serais ravie de m'occuper des vôtres.

I'm 27 years old nanny living in Paris. I'm currently an aupair for a wonderful French-American family with two boys age 8 and 5. I will be available to work from October 2021. If you find me a suitable candidate, don't hesitate to contact me for further interview. 

Thank you.

J’aime passer du temps avec les enfants, jouer avec eux, les amener au parc, faire les devoirs avec eux, leur donner un bain, etc. Je fais preuve d’optimisme et d’optimisme. Je suis bilingue - anglais/français et j’apprends l’espagnol. Je pourrai aider vos enfants à apprendre/améliorer l’anglais. Pour mon passe-temps, j’aime faire du vélo, coudre, lire, cuisiner et explorer de nouveaux endroits.

Je suis ponctuelle, sérieuse, et très responsable et je prendrai bien soin de vos enfants et je ferai en sorte que nous passions de très bons moments ensemble.

Bonjour,

Through my work in Child Protection, I cared for many children ages 0-17, who had been removed from their parents care. It was challenging, yet incredibly rewarding to help children with developmental delays eventually meet their milestones. 
As of January 2022, I have been regularly working as a Nanny in Paris for two children.

I used to help prepare his meals, change his diapers and put him to sleep. Now, I mostly help him with home works and do activities with him. Last year I had a 6 months Au pair experience in Berlin where I took care of two little girls aged, respectively, 3 years and 10 months. During the summer, I was a nanny in Zurich and looked after two children of 3 and 4 years old. Even though they require a lot of patience and care, I wholeheartedly believe that children are the purest thing that is on earth and find really liking spending my free time with them, thus why I used to babysit as well and have 3 years of paid experience. Sécurité avant tout : Formée aux premiers secours, je veille à ce que les enfants évoluent dans un environnement sûr.
Activités éducatives : Je propose des jeux et activités créatives adaptés à leur âge pour stimuler leur développement.
Soutien scolaire : J’aide les enfants à faire leurs devoirs, en créant un cadre de travail calme et structuré.
